{"tid":1788213,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 大家嘅facebook可能已經俾政府收集晒","createTime":"2019-12-18T13:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T13:39:49.000Z","uid":124144,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e334bfcd44322d89ce11a719f20939e6ba2da3c6","tid":1788213,"uid":124144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T13:14:05.000Z","msg":"唔知大家發唔發覺近排香港政府出咗好多<span style=\"color: green;\">on9 facebook公關</span>，例如之前<span style=\"color: orange;\">黑警蒙面食飯，遲啲林奠又開fb live，邱騰華開facebook live，膠紙貼催淚彈等等</span>。 <span style=\"color: green;\">當大家好開心俾嬲嬲嘅時候</span>有冇諗過<span style=\"color: red;\">政府喺facebook睇到邊個account俾嬲嬲，之後就mark底晒大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，之後再起你底</span>，就算唔捉你都可以black list你，下次去支那澳門市嘅時候搞鳩你。<br />\n<br />\n你可能話：屌啦，政府啲IT咁on9點會搞咁多嘢呀<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">對於政府嚟講，開fb live已經係一個好新奇好創新好勁嘅文宣，搞呢個咁勁咁新奇嘅文宣一定會搵PR公司，PR公司應該都會同佢分析到即使佢開fb live都唔會R到幾多民意，但係佢哋仍然開fb live</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">TLDR結論：唔好用自己用開嘅facebook account狗衝入政府啲on9 page俾嬲嬲，如果想俾嬲嬲嘅唔該開個分身入去俾嬲嬲，當然如果可以嘅盡量冷處理，政府啲on9文宣冇營養，一陣推下推下俾啲無腦港豬friend睇到就唔好</span></span>"},{"pid":"d60159bf32e2ddfe0c26ca237f783a7de9ebd80d","tid":1788213,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T13:15:29.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[你今日FC咗未] 全港最大的Fact Check平台已經推出了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776631</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7154ce42ecf2844840ec7e5fb5133ebf15adb29c","tid":1788213,"uid":124144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T13:15:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"37f76129427ac7a7d2319b3bc554eed6cbb7b8d3","tid":1788213,"uid":176164,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e334bfcd44322d89ce11a719f20939e6ba2da3c6","tid":1788213,"uid"